# About me

I'm Le Bao Nguyen (Nguyen is the last name), a student+developer
from Viet Nam.

I was born in 2008.

I like technology, music, and sometimes writing stuff to keep
this page alive (while nobody even knows this exists).

My (contributed) softwares are normally not something too big,
or never reaches to its finish stage because of me developing it
<i>alone</i>.

There is no main language here. I work on many language, some
have their own version that are fine, some however do not.
Pretty much that I'm struggling here. You'll see some of my
projects using the link below.

# What this page has?

Tutorials, announcements and my own opinion about things.

My associated projects are here too.

Maybe some other stuff too? I don't know:)

# Reporting bugs

The page is not bug-free. There is no proper small screen support (yet?).

If you found anything weird, tell me in this <a href="https://github.com/lebao3105/lebao3105.github.io/issues">page</a>.
